    "39219065": {
      "title": "Waterloo-Stanford group scale of hypnotic susceptibility, form C: manual and response booklet",
      "abstract": "Abstract The manual and response booklet for the Waterloo-Stanford Group Scale of Hypnotic Susceptibility, Form C (WSGC) is presented. The WSGC is a group adaptation of the individually administered Stanford Hypnotic Susceptibility Scale, Form C (SHSS:C)."
